===Format===
* '''OneGame Pro Championship - Season 2''' - '' February 26th - March 19th, 2025
** 64 teams
*** 24 invited teams
*** 40 teams from Open Qualifiers
** Squad, {{Abbr/TPP}}
* '''Pre Quarters'''
** 64 teams
** Teams are divided into 4 groups of 16 teams each
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 12 teams}} from each group qualify for ''Quarter Finals
* '''Quarter Finals''' - ''February 26th, March 3rd-4th
** 48 teams
** Teams are divided into 3 groups of 16 teams each
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from each group qualify for ''Semi Finals
* '''Semi Finals''' - ''March 5th, 10th and 13th
** 24 teams
** Teams are divided into 3 groups of 8 teams each
** Round-robin format
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} qualify for ''Grand Finals
* '''Grand Finals''' - ''March 14th, 17th-19th
** 16 teams
** 4 matchdays

